Installation instructions:

1. Install prerequisite Perl modules:
   * X11::FullScreen
   * Time::Duration
   * Video::Xine
   * App::Config
   * Image::Imlib2

2. Install prerequisite Unix libraries and packages:
   * xine-lib
   * postgres
   * postgres-perl

(Hopefully all of the above can be handled by an RPM install)

3. Start Postgres

4. Run the Postgres installation script

For PHP:

5. Install prerequisite packages:
  * apache
  * php

6. Run the PHP installation script
